OL,3,CWoman denied NHS IVF because husband
OL,4,Chas children 'punished'
OL,6,FA woman who is unable to conceive
OL,7,Fnaturally says she feels "punished"
OL,8,Fafter being denied NHS fertility
OL,9,Ftreatment because her husband already
OL,10,Fhad children.
OL,12,FHeidi - who did not want to give her
OL,13,Flast name - said she has wanted to be
OL,14,Fa mother for as long as she could
OL,15,Fremember but, due to health issues,
OL,16,Fhad been left with IVF as her best
OL,17,Foption.
