OL,3,CWoman denied NHS IVF because husband
OL,4,Chas children 'punished'
OL,6,FBut because her husband has children
OL,7,Ffrom a previous relationship the NHS
OL,8,Fin Lincolnshire will not fund the
OL,9,Ftreatment.
OL,11,FHeidi said: "It makes me sad. It makes
OL,12,Fme angry as well. I think I go through
OL,13,Fquite a lot of emotions with it.
OL,15,F"Why can't I be allowed that like
OL,16,Fevery other woman? Just because my
OL,17,Fhusband has children from a previous
OL,18,Fmarriage? Why shouldn't I be allowed
OL,19,Fthat?"
OL,21,FWho can get IVF treatment on the NHS?
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/8
