OL,3,CWoman denied NHS IVF because husband
OL,4,Chas children 'punished'
OL,6,FThe NHS says health trusts across
OL,7,FEngland and Wales are working to
OL,8,Fprovide the same levels of service.
OL,10,FBut rules around IVF differ across the
OL,11,Fcountry and often depend on local
OL,12,Fpolicies.
OL,14,FIntegrated care boards (ICBs) may have
OL,15,Fadditional criteria people need to
OL,16,Fmeet before they can have IVF on the
OL,17,FNHS, such as not having any children
OL,18,Falready, from current or previous
OL,19,Frelationships; being a healthy weight;
OL,20,Fnot smoking; or being under a certain
OL,21,Fage.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/8
