OL,3,CWoman denied NHS IVF because husband
OL,4,Chas children 'punished'
OL,6,FAlthough up to three cycles of IVF are
OL,7,Frecommended, some ICBs only offer one
OL,8,Fcycle, or only offer NHS-funded IVF in
OL,9,Fexceptional circumstances.
OL,11,FCampaigners in Lincolnshire claim
OL,12,Fcouples are facing a "postcode
OL,13,Flottery" when it comes to accessing
OL,14,Ftreatment.
OL,16,FCouple Sarah and Chris Curtiss are
OL,17,Fexpecting a baby after trying for
OL,18,Feight years.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/8
