OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F364A1734101042
OL,3,CWoman denied NHS IVF because husband
OL,4,Chas children 'punished'
OL,6,FThey had been told their chances of
OL,7,Fconceiving naturally were slim and
OL,8,Fwere unable to get IVF on the NHS
OL,9,Fbecause Chris already has a child from
OL,10,Fa previous relationship.
OL,12,FThey have been campaigning for years
OL,13,Ffor a change in the rules to allow
OL,14,Fgreater access to infertility
OL,15,Ftreatment for couples in the same
OL,16,Fsituation.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/8
