OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F364A1734101042
OL,3,CWoman denied NHS IVF because husband
OL,4,Chas children 'punished'
OL,6,FSarah said: "I have a fantastic
OL,7,Frelationship with my step daughter I
OL,8,Fabsolutely love her to pieces but that
OL,9,Fdoesn't ever, and hasn't ever, stopped
OL,10,Fme wanting a child of my own as well
OL,11,Fand to bring a child into this family
OL,12,Funit is the missing puzzle piece for
OL,13,Fus."
OL,15,FWhile Sarah and Chris have managed to
OL,16,Fconceive naturally, Heidi worries that
OL,17,Fwithout access to IVF she may never
OL,18,Fbecome a mother.
OL,20,FShe said: "I do feel like I'm being
OL,21,Fpunished."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G6/8
