OL,3,CWoman denied NHS IVF because husband
OL,4,Chas children 'punished'
OL,6,FPeople in the East Midlands are now
OL,7,Fbeing asked for their view on the
OL,8,Ffuture of NHS IVF services, but the
OL,9,Fpolicy which has affected Sarah,
OL,10,FChris, Heidi and her husband could
OL,11,Fremain the same.
OL,13,FChris describes the current system as
OL,14,Fan "emotional rollercoaster", adding:
OL,15,F"Just because I'm lucky enough to be a
OL,16,Ffather to someone else's child, why
OL,17,Fdoes my wife now have the inability to
OL,18,Freceive the support that she deserves?
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G7/8
