OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F364A1734101042
OL,3,CWoman denied NHS IVF because husband
OL,4,Chas children 'punished'
OL,6,F"And its not just about us and our
OL,7,Ffamily this is about families up and
OL,8,Fdown the country."
OL,10,FNHS Lincolnshire's Integrated Care
OL,11,FBoard said no decisions have been made
OL,12,Fand it was "aware of strength of
OL,13,Ffeelings" around fertility treatments.
OL,15,FIt said the views of those who filled
OL,16,Fout the online survey would inform the
OL,17,Ffinal policy.
